commit.message: Modify deployment to match Hack NC project.

Add domain name to deployment.

Deployments are now accessible using a custom hostname rather than by IP
address. Deployments on the 'production' workspace are accessible at
api.ultimanager.com, and other deploys are accessible at
<terraform-workspace>.api.ultimanager.com.

Configure NGINX webserver.

NGINX is now configured to serve static files and proxy other requests
to the gunicorn application.

Configure Django provisioning.

The configuration process now includes running Django specific tasks
such as database migrations and static file collection.

Rename django role to 'python-app'.

The role is responsible for fetching a python application and installing
its dependencies without any Django specific tasks.

Add Ansible role to pull source code.

So far, Ansible pulls in the application source code and installs the
requirements into a virtualenv.
